Velveting
- coat meat with baking soda + salt
- or coat meat with soy sauce + starch + oil + sugar
- marinate for few hours
- blanch shortly in boiling water
- or cook shortly on hot oil

Proofing: allowing dough to rest and rise
Scoville scale: measurement of chili pepper spiciness, capsaicin concentration
- Scoville heat units (SHU):
- Carolina reaper: 2M SHU
- Ghost pepper: 1M SHU
- Habanero: 200k SHU
- Tabasco: 40k SHU
- Cayenne: 40k SHU
- Jalapeño: 5k SHU

#Knife
Japan
- Santoku: all-purpose, flat
- Gyuto: meat, curved
- Nakiri: vegetables, rectangular, thin
- Deba: fish, curved, thick
Western
- Chef's knife: all-purpose, curved
- Bread knife: serrated
- Fillet knife: fish, thin, flexible
- Cleaver: chopping, rectangular, thick
